name: _ dog walk feeder
description:
this is the feeder pilar (UK) or power box (US) on my dog walk route. it is a cabinet for electrical equipment, which is usually mounted in the street and controlling the electrical supply to a number of houses in a neighborhood. 

all feeders you will find in the open wild have a unique patina due to weather influences, stickers, tags, grafitti, or paintings etc and tell an often overseen story.

this model has been used in my tile in #layerbreaker
